Lokaci na Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A yammacin yau a birnin Willing, West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wani babban kadara na kamfanin.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wuraren da ake kira Tennessee da Mississippi.
A lokacin da ya amince da zaben don kammala zaben Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi kokarin kara goyon bayan zaben ta tsakiya da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a kan majalisa idan aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne Trump zai fara jawabinsa a West Virginia da yamma, kuma ta yaya za mu kalli shi a Intanet?
A ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 ne za a yi jawabin Trump a birnin Willing, West Virginia, da aka shirya a karfe 7 na dare.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa a YouTube.
Ana tsammanin Trump zai yi sauraron karar takararsa a Kotun Koli a wannan makon, na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke da matsala game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da amincewa a Majalisar Dattawa a cikin mako guda yayin binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan jawabin shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, kamfen din Shugaba Trump ya sanar da cewa jawabai biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin karfafa ayyukan masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa da majalisar dokoki yana da mahimmanci ga tsarinsa, cewa shugaban zai tafi jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu, yayin da muke shiga cikin mawuyacin lokacin yakin neman zabe", wani wakilin Trump ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Willing, taron na yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji The West Virginia Metro News.
Asabar ne karo na biyu da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya ci nasara da sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morris, wanda shine shugaban binciken.
Wannan ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morris ba cewa shugaban kasa ya kamata ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi turawa a cikin binciken ,  ya ce Simon Hedar, masanin siyasa daga Jami'ar West Virginia, rahoton Reuters.
