Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani wanda zai zama abokin hamayyar Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon shiri na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda aka gina akan dandamali na Berners-Lee Solid.
