Yana iya samun jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, fanatik, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna samuwa a lokaci guda a cikin mai bincike guda.
