Fadar White House ta ce za a iya dage taron Trump da Rosenstein
Babban taron Donald Trump da Mataimakin Babban Shari'a Rod Rosenstein na iya jinkirta har mako guda yayin da ake gwagwarmaya game da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wani wakilin fadar White House ya bayyana a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke nazarin tsoma baki a cikin zaɓen Rasha, alaƙar mataimakan Trump da Rasha, da yiwuwar cikas ga shari'a ta shugaban kasa.
Ko Trump ya kori mataimakin babban mai gabatar da kara ko a'a, don haka ya sa 'yancin kai na Mueller ya kasance cikin barazana, yana zuba mai a cikin wutar Washington na watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein yana tattaunawa game da yiwuwar ɗaukar makirufo don yin rikodin tattaunawar da ya yi da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar sa a ajiye shugaban kasa a karkashin Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya tafi fadar White House a cikin jita-jita cewa zai yi murabus.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da cewa za a yi ganawa da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yana zaune a hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce ba zai so ya kori Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka soke taron don kauce wa rikici a gaban majalisar dokokin kasar, inda Kavanaugh da wata mace da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr. Christina Blassy Ford, suka halarci taron.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba da umarnin gudanar da bincike na mako guda na FBI kan sanarwa da aka yi wa Kavana, wanda ya kara jinkirta zaben a majalisar dattawa.
Sakataren labarai na Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a shirin Fox News Sunday.
Lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da ganawa da Rosenstein, ta ce, "Ba a sanya kwanan wata ba, watakila a wannan makon, watakila a gaba. Ina tsammanin, watakila a mako guda daga baya, la'akari da duk sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin Kotun Koli.
Amma duk abin da zai faru, kuma ina ba da labarai mafi kyau.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yarda su kalubalanci cewa Sanders ba ta gudanar da gabatarwa ga manema labarai a fadar White House tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Chris Wallace ya tambaye ta dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta ce rashin samun labarai na labarai na sa ta yi watsi da 'yan jarida da ke aiki a cikin jama'a, ko da yake ta kara da cewa: "Na yarda da cewa suna aiki a cikin jama'a".
Sai ta ce, za a kara samun Trump da manema labarai.
