Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Jami'ai sun ce akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa garin Palau a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga hukumar rigakafin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palau, wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga garin Palo bayan bala'in da ya faru.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Paul da Dongla a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala  wani yanki ne wanda ke shimfidawa a cikin fiye da mil 180 (300 km) na rairayin bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regency  wani yanki ne na gwamnati wanda ke da matsayi a ƙasa da lardin, a shekara ta 2017 yana da mutane 299,200.
Kifi da kuma noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiya na Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Harkokin nickel na da mahimmanci ga lardin, amma galibi suna da yawa a Moraval, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Indonesiya ta rage bala'i ta gano cewa, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palo da Donggala sun sha wahala sau da yawa daga tsunami.
A shekarar 1938, tsunami a birnin Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200, kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific mai girgizar kasa da kuma tashin hankali kuma tana fuskantar girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a ƙasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a duk faɗin tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a gabar yamma ta Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris zuwa farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudu da Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar kudu, wanda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: A garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.6 ta faru.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mantawa a wajen Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawo har zuwa mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai rauni ta afkawa yankin Pidi Jai a lardin Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, tun da ya tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar da ta faru a sakamakon girgizar kasa ta 2004 da tsunami.
A wannan lokacin, tsunami bai zo ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a tsibirin yawon shakatawa na Lombok na Indonesia, wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido ba tare da damar fita ba.
