A farkon yakin cinikayya tsakanin China da Amurka ya kasance mai ban tsoro, kuma tun da yake yakin ya yi nisa daga ƙarshe, a cikin dogon lokaci rashin fahimtar juna tsakanin ƙasashe na iya zama fa'ida ga Beijing, masana sun ce.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekara, yana biyan haraji kan manyan kayayyakin fitarwa na kasar Sin, ciki har da allon hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi yawan tashin hankali ya faru a wannan makon, lokacin da sabbin kudade suka shafi kayayyaki na dala biliyan 200, kuma sun biya rabin harajin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da Beijing ta amsa ta hanyar da ta yi, ta ƙara haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari na kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin mayar da martani ga Amurka, kuma ba za ta iya ba da amsa ba ga tattalin arzikinta na biyu.
Don sa Washington ta janye, dole ne mu zurfafa cikin bukatar, amma nuna sha'awar Amurka a fili ba shi da kyau ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da wannan halin da ake ciki, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci, yana rage dogaro tsakanin kasashen biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani gaggawa da aka yi a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da mummunan tattalin arziki ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura suka yi imani", in ji Abigail Grace, mataimakin mai bincike na Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Tsaro na Amurka.
Syria a shirye don 'yan gudun hijira dawo, ya ce Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta ce tana shirye don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira kuma ta nemi taimako wajen sake gina kasar da yaki ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai yana lalata.
Da yake magana da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Mu'al ya ce yanayin kasar yana inganta.
"Yanzu, halin da ake ciki a kasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro, saboda ci gaba da ake samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da mayar da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin su koma rayuwa ta al'ada.
Yanzu muna da dukkan yanayi don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira zuwa kasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma tattalin arziki da aka yi niyya da nufin inganta rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma hanyoyin rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce fiye da mutane miliyan biyar da biyar ne suka bar kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a 2011.
Akwai wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Mu'allam ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi farin cikin karbar taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta rushe.
Duk da haka, ya kara da cewa kasar ba za ta karbi taimako ba a musayar wasu yanayi ko taimako daga kasashen da ke tallafawa 'yan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Rider a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018, ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka da lambar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin Le Golf National a cikin birni na Paris, Faransa.
Wannan ne karo na shida da Amurka ta yi asara a kan Turai kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta samu lambar yabo a lokacin da tawagar dan Denmark Thomas Björn ta samu maki 14.5, wanda ya dace domin ta ci Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi gwagwarmaya a gasar, ya jefa kwallonsa cikin ruwa a 3 da 16th moon, ya bar wannan wasan na Francesco Malinar.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya, Malinari, ya yi kyau sosai a duk zagaye, ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka wuce wannan filin da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara wasan a cikin tsarin yanzu a 1979.
Dan Amurka Jordan Spice ya ci nasara da maki 5 da 4 da dan wasan da ya fi kasa a tawagar Turai, Thorneburn Olsen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, babban dan wasan duniya, ya yi nasara 2 da 1 a kan Ian Pawlter na Ingila, wanda zai iya yin wasa a cikin Ryder Cup na karshe.
Tsohon tsohon soja na gasar cin kofin Ryder na Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan da ya fi kowa nasara a gasar tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
