Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan shi ne babban tarihin daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14, kuma ya fi Jack Nicklaus baya a wannan matsayi.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya da juna, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tinnie Finnow, waɗanda suka yi wasa a duk lokacin gasar a golf mai kyau.
