Bayani na ruwan sama na ja: Rashin taro a Pinellas, Monati da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga kwamitin kula da kifi da namun daji na Florida ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan Red Tide ya ragu a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar rahoton da kwamitin ya bayar, an samu wasu wuraren da ke da ci gaba a yankin Pinellas, Manati, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke nuna cewa an rage yawan abubuwan da ke faruwa.
Ruwa na ruwan ruwan Red tide yana gudana kimanin mil 130 (200 km) na rairayin bakin teku daga arewacin yankin Pinellas zuwa kudancin yankin Lee.
Ana iya samun 'ya'yan furen a kusan mil 10 daga bakin teku a gundumar Hillsborough, amma yawan su ya ragu a makonni da suka gabata.
An kuma ga wani ruwan sama mai launin ruwan kasa a yankin Pasca.
Matsakaicin girman taro a kan rairayin bakin teku ko kusa da rairayin bakin teku a Pinellas County aka lura a makon da ya gabata, a Hillsborough taro ya kasance daga low to high. a Monato na bango zuwa high, a kan rairayin bakin teku ko kusa da rairayin bakin teku a Saratoga County taro ya kasance daga bango zuwa high, a Charlotte County daga bango zuwa tsakiyar, a kan rairayin bakin teku ko kusa da rairayin bakin teku a Li County daga bango zuwa high da kuma a Cooley County low taro.
An ruwaito cewa akwai tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin numfashi a cikin gundumar Pinellas, Monati, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani rahoto game da tashin hankali na iska daga arewa maso yammacin Florida.
